  "timeline": [
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_001",
      "segment_index": 1,
      "text": "AI 时代，真正拉开差距的不是数据，是复盘能力。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_001.wav",
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.44,
      "duration": 3.44,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_002",
      "segment_index": 2,
      "text": "我这条视频只有 141 播放，2 秒跳出接近 50%。如果只看播放，这条很差。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_002.wav",
      "start": 3.66,
      "end": 10.94,
      "duration": 7.28,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_003",
      "segment_index": 3,
      "text": "但如果认真复盘，它反而告诉我：下一条最该先改的，不是方向，而是开头。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_003.wav",
      "start": 11.16,
      "end": 17.0,
      "duration": 5.84,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_004",
      "segment_index": 4,
      "text": "很多人现在用 AI 做内容，最大的问题不是不会生成。而是数据回来以后，还是只会问一句：这条是不是废了？",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_004.wav",
      "start": 17.28,
      "end": 24.16,
      "duration": 6.88,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_005",
      "segment_index": 5,
      "text": "播放低，就怀疑选题。点赞少，就怀疑表达。没人私信，就怀疑方向。但这样复盘，其实没用。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_005.wav",
      "start": 24.44,
      "end": 31.96,
      "duration": 7.52,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_006",
      "segment_index": 6,
      "text": "因为数据本身不会告诉你答案。真正有用的是，你能不能从数据里拆出问题层级。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_006.wav",
      "start": 32.18,
      "end": 38.18,
      "duration": 6.0,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_007",
      "segment_index": 7,
      "text": "比如我这条视频，推荐页其实给过一点入口。但 2 秒跳出接近 50%，5 秒完播也不高。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_007.wav",
      "start": 38.4,
      "end": 46.8,
      "duration": 8.4,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_008",
      "segment_index": 8,
      "text": "这说明什么？它不一定说明方向错了。更可能说明，用户第一眼还没明白这条视频跟他有什么关系，就已经划走了。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_008.wav",
      "start": 47.02,
      "end": 54.7,
      "duration": 7.68,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_009",
      "segment_index": 9,
      "text": "所以我下一条不该先换方向。也不该先换人群。更不该整条推翻重写。我只先改一个变量：开头 5 秒。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_009.wav",
      "start": 54.98,
      "end": 66.42,
      "duration": 11.44,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_010",
      "segment_index": 10,
      "text": "这就是我现在对 AI 最大的理解。AI 不是帮你列一堆 KPI 的。什么播放量、点赞率、收藏率、完播率，看着很完整。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_010.wav",
      "start": 66.7,
      "end": 75.66,
      "duration": 8.96,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_011",
      "segment_index": 11,
      "text": "但如果这些数字最后不能告诉你下一步该改哪里，那它们只是一个好看的表。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_011.wav",
      "start": 75.88,
      "end": 80.44,
      "duration": 4.56,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_012",
      "segment_index": 12,
      "text": "真正有用的复盘，应该逼你回答三个问题：第一，哪一层出了问题？是标题、开头、中段结构，还是结尾承接？",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_012.wav",
      "start": 80.66,
      "end": 88.9,
      "duration": 8.24,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_013",
      "segment_index": 13,
      "text": "第二，下一条只改哪个变量？不要一条数据不好，就标题、选题、结构、人群全都改。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_013.wav",
      "start": 89.18,
      "end": 96.94,
      "duration": 7.76,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_014",
      "segment_index": 14,
      "text": "第三，改完以后看哪个指标？改开头，就看 2 秒跳出、3 秒留存、5 秒完播。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_014.wav",
      "start": 97.22,
      "end": 104.5,
      "duration": 7.28,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_015",
      "segment_index": 15,
      "text": "改中段，就看平均观看和完播。改承接，就看收藏、评论、私信和主页访问。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_015.wav",
      "start": 104.78,
      "end": 112.46,
      "duration": 7.68,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_016",
      "segment_index": 16,
      "text": "这条视频虽然播放低，但它还有 3 个收藏。这说明内容不一定完全没价值。更像是价值出现得太晚，用户前面没被接住。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_016.wav",
      "start": 112.68,
      "end": 121.48,
      "duration": 8.8,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_017",
      "segment_index": 17,
      "text": "所以我下一条最该做的，不是证明我这个方向有多对。而是先把开头改到用户愿意留下来看。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_017.wav",
      "start": 121.7,
      "end": 128.42,
      "duration": 6.72,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_018",
      "segment_index": 18,
      "text": "播放是入口。收藏是认可。私信要评分。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_018.wav",
      "start": 128.64,
      "end": 132.48,
      "duration": 3.84,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_019",
      "segment_index": 19,
      "text": "但真正拉开差距的，不是你有没有数据。而是数据差的时候，你能不能看出问题在哪。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_019.wav",
      "start": 132.7,
      "end": 139.34,
      "duration": 6.64,
      "pause_after": 0.22
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_020",
      "segment_index": 20,
      "text": "如果每条内容发完，你都能知道下一条只改哪一个变量。那你就不是在碰运气。你是在迭代。",
      "audio_path": "dist/third_episode_real_review_scene_candidate/tts_segments/seg_020.wav",
      "start": 139.56,
      "end": 146.2,
      "duration": 6.64,
      "pause_after": 0.15
    }
  ]
